fees-3497182">公布了新的运行时费用</a>，一旦客户的游戏安装量和终身收入突破了一定的门槛，该费用就会对客户生效。</p><p>然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-backlash-explained-why-game-developers-are-speaking-out-on-twitter-3497816">游戏开发商对这些变化的反应却是灾难性的</a>。例如， <em>Terraria</em>的开发商 Re-Logic <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/terraria-developer-commits-over-200k-to-funding-unity-rivals-3500981">承诺向开源引擎 Godot 和 FNA 提供 20 万美元，</a>为小型工作室提供其他机会。</p><p>另外 500 名开发者表达了他们的失望之情，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/over-500-developers-are-protesting-unity-by-demonetising-their-games-3500464">将自己的游戏取消货币化</a>，阻止 Unity 获得任何收入，直到他们觉得自己的意见得到了倾听。 </p><figure id="attachment_3512365" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3512365" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3512365" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unity-ceo-steps-down-after-controversial-fee-rollout-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unity-ceo-steps-down-after-controversial-fee-rollout-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unity-ceo-steps-down-after-controversial-fee-rollout-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unity-ceo-steps-down-after-controversial-fee-rollout-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unity-ceo-steps-down-after-controversial-fee-rollout-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unity-ceo-steps-down-after-controversial-fee-rollout-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unity-ceo-steps-down-after-controversial-fee-rollout-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3512365" class="wp-caption-text"> 《羔羊崇拜》来源：Devolver Digital</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.morningstar.com/news/marketwatch/20230913576/unity-softwares-new-game-developer-fees-result-in-pr-disaster-stock-falls">一位分析师将其描述为一场“公关灾难”</a> ，而其他人则对这些变化引起的“愤怒”表示同情，但补充说，Unity 的价格和价值“长期以来一直有利于开发人员”。</p><p>上月底，Unity Create 总裁 Marc Whitten 根据对原版的反应，透露了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-makes-changes-to-controversial-runtime-fees-after-hearing-concerns-3503635">对运行时费用的修改</a>。</p><p>这些变化包括自行向 Unity 报告游戏安装量，而费用将是游戏每月收入 2.5% 的削减或使用游戏每月参与度数据计算出的金额中的较低者。</p><p>其他游戏新闻方面，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision-blizzard">动视暴雪</a>表示，由于微软的收购尚未最终确定， <em>《使命召唤：现代战争 3》</em>或<em>《暗黑破坏神 4》</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3-and-diablo-4-wont-be-coming-to-game-pass-this-year-3512288">今年不会登陆 Game Pass</a> 。</p><p>在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-ceo-john-riccitiello-steps-down-after-disastrous-fee-proposals-3512336">灾难性的费用提案后，Unity 后任首席执行官 John Riccitiello 辞职</a>。</p> ;
